      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DWPDB85DEmA/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.82787-15/656808971_18442129354112163_542398369949918257_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e35_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=101&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg1OTMxNjE4MzUyNzEwMDI2OA%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjEwODB4MTQ0MC5zZHIuQzMifQ%3D%3D&amp;_nc_ohc=6aLg6cAF8fAQ7kNvwFD7bNf&amp;_nc_oc=Adp1gis3f5k_DTbLj8aL_OjY3dtmpDc36OWGXSsyfJKlX925qZ-aChlX8xKFHABfN6k&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=7&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=8CBsPUc6BCXyicSrNbz4jg&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfxfllFVaARgm-d28eUfV7eiBsnMBG0sFJ8xPiVCaPzQ2Q&amp;oe=69C8EE15" alt="Instagram billede fra @damienhirst" /></p><p><strong>@damienhirst</strong></p><p>Introducing: The ‘Triple Trouble’ catalogue 📚<br/>
<br/>
Published to accompany the exhibition of the same name, this catalogue documents individual and collaborative works by @obeygiant, @damienhirst, and @invaderwashere.<br/>
<br/>
Presenting all works from the show in full-colour reproduction, it showcases familiar motifs, such as Fairey’s Obey iconography, Hirst’s spots and cabinets and Invader’s Space Invader mosaics, reconfigured in provocative and playful ways.<br/>
<br/>
 📍Explore the book via our link in bio.<br/>
<br/>
🖼️ Don’t miss your chance to see the artworks in person, at the ‘Triple Trouble’ exhibition at Newport Street Gallery. The show is running until 29 March.<br/>
<br/>
🎨 Original artworks from the exhibition are available by application on HENI Primary via our link in bio until 29 March.<br/>
<br/>
#HENI #Art #ArtBook #TripleTrouble #Exhibition</p>]]></description>
